output:
Twinkling lights of red and green
It's Christmas time, it must be seen
Snowflakes drift from up on high
Creating wintertime bliss in the sky

Homes adorned with holly and pine
Families gather around the tree twine
Chestnuts roasting on the fire
Glad hearts await the holiday sire

Carols echo in the night
Laughter fills a joyful sight
The candle's light shines ever bright
A Christmas miracle, a wondrous delight
